org.apache.calcite.adapter.enumerable

接口 NestedBlockBuilder

  • 所有已知子接口:
    AggAddContext, AggResetContext, AggResultContext, WinAggAddContext, WinAggResetContext, WinAggResultContext
    所有已知实现类:
    AggAddContextImpl, AggResetContextImpl, AggResultContextImpl, NestedBlockBuilderImpl, WinAggAddContextImpl, WinAggResetContextImpl, WinAggResultContextImpl

    public interface NestedBlockBuilder
    Allows to build nested code blocks with tracking of current context and the nullability of particular RexNode expressions.
    另请参阅:
    StrictAggImplementor.implementAdd(AggContext, AggAddContext)

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 实例方法 抽象方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      BlockBuilder currentBlock()
      Returns the current code block
      Map<RexNode,Boolean> currentNullables()
      Returns the current nullability state of rex nodes.
      void exitBlock()
      Leaves the current code block.
      BlockBuilder nestBlock()
      Starts nested code block.
      void nestBlock(BlockBuilder block)
      Uses given block as the new code context.

    • 方法详细资料

      • nestBlock

        BlockBuilder nestBlock()
        Starts nested code block. The resulting block can optimize expressions and reuse already calculated values from the parent blocks.
        返回:
        new code block that can optimize expressions and reuse already calculated values from the parent blocks.

      • nestBlock

        void nestBlock(BlockBuilder block)
        Uses given block as the new code context. The current block will be restored after exitBlock() call.
        参数:
        block - new code block
        另请参阅:
        exitBlock()

      • nestBlock

        void nestBlock(BlockBuilder block,
               Map<RexNode,Boolean> nullables)
        Uses given block as the new code context and the map of nullability. The current block will be restored after exitBlock() call.
        参数:
        block - new code block
        nullables - map of expression to its nullability state
        另请参阅:
        exitBlock()

      • currentBlock

        BlockBuilder currentBlock()
        Returns the current code block
        返回:
        current code block

      • currentNullables

        Map<RexNode,Boolean> currentNullables()
        Returns the current nullability state of rex nodes. The resulting value is the summary of all the maps in the block hierarchy.
        返回:
        current nullability state of rex nodes

      • exitBlock

        void exitBlock()
        Leaves the current code block.
        另请参阅:
        nestBlock()
